nnot be neglected. We\ncomment on how the approximations used in this paper, in particular the\nassumption of spherical symmetry, could change quantitatively our conclusions\nand might provide a better explanation for the CMB CS.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 7 May 2014 10:06:59 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Thu, 8 May 2014 12:52:48 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Thu, 3 Sep 2015 14:06:05 GMT"}],"update_date":"2017-03-22"}
