effect. Our results provide,\nin particular, the basis for a theory of skyrmion caloritronics for a dilute\nskyrmion gas in clean insulating chiral magnets.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 7 May 2014 10:53:35 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Thu, 8 May 2014 15:42:37 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Wed, 24 Sep 2014 13:56:22 GMT"}],"update_date":"2014-11-12"}
