ry epsilon-entropy, which corresponds to the\nclassical RDF with an additional causality or nonanticipative condition imposed\non the optimal reproduction conditional distribution.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 7 May 2014 13:00:46 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Wed, 18 Nov 2015 21:17:50 GMT"}],"update_date":"2016-11-17"}
